fields.name: Fossil Three-Hand Brown Leather Watch
fields.description: This Fossil Neutra Chrono men's watch combines tradtitional styling with a rugged, masculine nature. The brushed stainless steel casing surrounds a simple, multifunction cream dial, featuring a discreet date window and a mix of Roman numeral and baton hour markers. The brown leather strap provides durability and comfort, whilst maintaining a handsome style and feel.

fields.name: Emporio Armani AR2461 Men's Black Watch
fields.description: This Emporio Armani watch has a round face with a matt finish bezel and an analogue display. Paired with a leather band, it will easily match your style. It features a Japanese quartz movement mechanism, giving you the reliability that you need to keep on track. You will look great and exude confidence when you wear this Emporio Armani Sportivo watch

fields.name: Fossil Grant Men's Chronograph Brown Leather Strap Watch
fields.description: Fossil's Grant Chronograph watch oozes smart- casual style. Set on a rich brown leather strap, the chronograph dial is set on a black face with roman numeral hour markers. 3 inset subdials show hours, minutes and seconds

fields.name: Rider White Dial - Brown Leather Watch
fields.description: Modern elegance in our new Rider. The super flat watch case frames the timeless dial elegantly in white. With a handmade leather strap of finest cowhide, the Rider is a stylish companion for any occasion

fields.name: Tissot T-Sport Chrono watch 45mm
fields.description: The T-Sport Collection of Tissot watches offers all you could ever want in a sports watch. Built for durability, each guarantees decades of reliability; its resistant materials also allow you to track time both in and out of water. Better still, you can select the style that mirrors your taste. Select from chronograph, traditional and a host of other designs to secure the sports watch that's best for you

fields.name: Omega De Ville Tresor Men's Black Leather Strap Watch
fields.description: Characterised by its thin and elegant case, the Trésor line was first launched by OMEGA in 1949 and housed the legendary 30mm calibre. More than half a century later, it continues to impress with one of today’s most advanced mechanical movements. Boasting a 40mm stainless steel case, this Omega De Ville Trésor watch houses a silver tone dial with 18 carat white gold three-hand movement and indexes, and a date display at the 6 o'clock position. Finished with a smart black leather strap. Inside, this De Ville Trésor is powered by the OMEGA Co-Axial Master Chronometer Calibre 8910 and is certified at the industry’s highest standard of precision, chronometric performance and magnetic resistance

fields.name: Classics 43mm Mens Watch
fields.description: A classic three-counter men’s chronograph design with on-trend dial in anthracite grey. Built for the circuit but just as home in any urban context, for men who love speed and seek performance." Solid steel 43mm case, fitted bracelet and specially decorated case-back, fine brushed and polished to a luxury gleam, and built to withstand the full pressures of professional racing." White Super-LumiNova® lume on the indexes, hour and minute hands enhance the dial’s at-a-glance readability. As does the XXL counter at 6 o’clock and the signature oversized “12”." The steel bracelet has a double safety folding clasp to prevent accidental opening and a “Driver” extension for wearing over a racing suit.

fields.name: Black Yellow Gold Rolex Watch
fields.description: Beautiful classic gents stainless steel & 18ct yellow Gold Rolex Oyster Perpetual Datejust, newly cleaned and polished and now looking absolutely fabulous in every way.

fields.name: G-Timeless Watch
fields.description: Designed with a steel case and bracelet completed with a silver sunbrushed dial for a tonal look, a new addition to the G-Timeless collection is introduced for Pre-Fall 2019

fields.name: Calvin Klein Classic Too Ladies Bracelet Watch
fields.description: Sleek and chic, this Calvin Klein Classic Too ladies' watch features a round case with flat glass stainless steel, with silver tone line hour markings and co-ordinating hands. A simple yet smart stainless steel bracelet adorns the wrist, and this classic timepiece is water resistant up to 30 metres

fields.name: Rado Coupole Classic 41mm Watch
fields.description: Inspired by Rado timepieces from the 60s, the Coupole collection showcases distinctly vintage design elements with a contemporary twist." Beautifully housed within a 41mm Gold PVD stainless steel case and protected by sapphire crystal glass, this Rado Coupole watch presents a crisp white dial equipped with Gold-tone hands, index hour markers and minute markers around the rim." Driven by a powerful automatic movement and water resistant to 50 metres, this high-performance timepiece benefits from an 80-hour power reserve and fastens with a gold strap

fields.name: Montblanc Heritage Automatic Men's Black Leather Strap Watch
fields.description: Inspired by historical Minerva classic wristwatches from the 1940s and 1950s, the Montblanc Heritage family combines the elegance of watchmaking's past with today’s bold design codes and technology. The Montblanc Heritage Automatic comes in a 40mm stainless steel case with a silvery-white dial adorned with applied rhodium-coated Arabic numerals, dots as indexes and hands that are enhanced with Super-LumiNova*. The Montblanc Heritage Automatic is powered by Montblanc’s MB 24.27 automatic movement and is equipped with a black sfumato alligator strap coming from the Richemont Pelletteria in Florence, Italy

fields.name: Apple Watch Midnight Aluminium Case
fields.description: Apple Watch is a wearable smartwatch that allows users to accomplish a variety of tasks, including making phone calls, sending text messages and reading email.

fields.name: Citizen Eco-Drive Men's Stainless Steel Bracelet Watch
fields.description: This handsome men's Citizen watch, with a stainless steel case and bracelet, is perfectly complemented by the sophisticated deep blue dial. Set with silver tone hour markers, date window and water resistance up to 100 metres; perfect for the modern day businessman. Featuring Citizen's award-winning Eco-Drive technology which harnesses both natural and artificial light and converts it into energy to power the watch - a watch that never needs a battery

fields.name: Montblanc 1858 Men’s Black Leather Strap Watch
fields.description: Inspired by watches conceived for military use and exploration, the Montblanc 1858 watch reinterprets these historical timepieces. This limited addition chronograph watch features a black calf leather strap for complete comfort, while the stainless steel case holds a sleek black dial complemented by historical beige luminescent cathedral-shaped hands and beige luminescent Arabic numerals. A legendary treasure to take you from A to B and way beyond. This watch is water resistant up to 100 metres.

fields.name: Montblanc Star Men’s Brown Leather Strap Watch
fields.description: Powered by traditional craftsmanship handed down from generation to generation, this brown leather strap watch from Montblanc was made for the modern man. A quality timepiece to treasure, it features an easy-to-read dial, handy date window and a subtle star design, while the sword hands powered by automatic movement will have you arriving right on time.

fields.name: Rolex - Oyster Perpetual 34
fields.description: The aesthetics of the Oyster Perpetual models set them apart as symbols of universal and classic style. They embody timeless form and function, firmly rooted in the pioneering origins of Rolex

fields.name: Rolex - Day Date 36
fields.description: The Oyster Perpetual Day Date 36 in 18 CT Yellow Gold with a white dial, flucted bezel and a president bracelet

fields.name: Jean Pierre Gold-Plated Double Hunter Skeleton Pocket Watch
fields.description: This double hunter watch by Jean Pierre has a beautifully embossed gold-plated case attached to a traditional gold-plated Albert chain. Its back opens to reveal a 17 jewelled mechanical movement with shock protection. A skeleton face, roman numerals

fields.name: Aspinall Double Fold Credit Card Holder
fields.description: A stylish alternative to a full-sized wallet, our Double Fold Credit Card Holder will slip comfortably into a back pocket or small handbag when you want to travel light." Handcrafted from the finest full-grain leather, the compact design has six credit card slots to keep your essentials organised.

fields.description: Stay organised in style with our Slim Credit Card Holder." Handcrafted from the finest full-grain leather, the design features four external card slots and a central pouch for an additional two cards or folded notes. Compact and lightweight, it will slip easily into a coat pocket or small handbag.

Paired with the Crucifix Pendant, you’re telling the world that you’re a leader - prepared to make the sacrifices needed to get you to where you are destined to be

It pushes you over the start line, propels you forward, and celebrates with you at the finish. And it’s there to start the cycle again. And again. And again." Wearing our Rose Pendant is your reminder to ignite your passion
